headline: Live Nation’s growth still strong even at record highs, Moffett starts at Buy
summary: Investing.com -- Moffett Nathanson began coverage of Live Nation with a Buy rating and a $195 price target saying that even with the stock near all-time highs, the company’s earnings can continue to grow at a double-digit pace as live music demand expands globally.
